{"tid":20337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界第二好味蜜瓜包到港　溫暖麵包夾雪糕要用飲管吸","createTime":"2016-12-03T10:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T12:21:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01a817ed8cf54a2dc462cedf2c1bf3129790209b","tid":20337,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161203/org/1480693765_d84a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161203%2Forg%2F1480693765_d84a.jpg&h=10b00065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/02/3222106/20161203_Vsub81AD_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F3222106%2F20161203_Vsub81AD_clean_w.mp4&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=bd025485\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/02/3222106/20161203_Vsub81AD_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161203/large/03sub81new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161203%2Flarge%2F03sub81new1.jpg&h=30a5d317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 香港店暫時推出三隻口味，保持雲呢拿、朱古力跟抹茶味，$38。 <br />\n <br />\n聽到世界第二好味蜜瓜包，第一個問題必然是，第一好味蜜瓜包又在哪兒？等等，蜜瓜包又是甚麼？這個來自日本的蜜瓜包跟菠蘿包一樣，外形十足蜜瓜一樣，中間夾住雪糕，其實沒有蜜瓜成份。 <br />\n <br />\n2014年在涉谷開店後大受歡迎，現時在日本已經有四十多間分店，在台灣亦設有分店，杜如風亦曾在節目中介紹過。店主認為教會自己蜜瓜包做法的師傅是第一名，因此開店時便謙稱自己的蜜瓜包是世界第二好吃。蜜瓜包最吸引的地方在於，溫暖鬆軟的包面包住半溶的雪糕，配合包上少許的曲奇皮，一次過能感受三種滋味。 <br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161203/large/03sub81new2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161203%2Flarge%2F03sub81new2.jpg&h=be2ad4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 店主梁家榮曾到金澤本店打工，滿師以後才回港開店。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161203/large/03sub81new3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161203%2Flarge%2F03sub81new3.jpg&h=7280d46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 店內裝修簡單，每當有麵包出爐便會用盤子敲打桌子。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n香港店將於十二月三日開張，暫時有雲呢拿、朱古力跟抹茶味，店家預計每天能賣六百個左右。<br />\n <br />\n世界第二好味雪糕蜜瓜麵包<br />\n地址：銅鑼灣景隆街15-27號地下1Ａ舖<br />\n <br />\n記者：李泳烔<br />\n攝影：周芝瑩 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nsource : <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=b08b3e73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&h=7a93f946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/</a><br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n幾得意喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbbd6026747b08f1343fbd5282c53e3b548aace","tid":20337,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0907c0f297ad7116e095ac7221bfc628c9feb465","tid":20337,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"原來唔係台灣野，上之去台灣見到，無人食嘅"},{"pid":"01a69cdf63c8d056ac9ceffba62dac2de2a0be35","tid":20337,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"去大阪果陣食過<br />\n唔錯"},{"pid":"1f9df0a148dd6ad19170b9ea6679402f1de80199","tid":20337,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T1